@Errol1886 We haven't received any other reports of this but we will keep our eyes peeled and see if we can reproduce and/or fix something on our end. 

It may have to do with having other applications open or something blocking the interaction with the device via USB. The web uses the U2F protocol while the desktop application using USB. Ledger also changed how they detect and support each of these (the user used to have to turn browser support ON or OFF but now no longer needs to.)

Again, we'll re-open this issue if we are able to re-produce or get further reports.
